    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    tinytex
SystemRequirements: LaTeX, pdflatex, pdfcrop,
    ImageMagick (optional for PNG output),
    pdf2svg (optional for SVG output)
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
